msgstr "Windows"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:777
msgid ""
"The configuration file is located at: `c:\\\\ProgramFiles\\\\Odoo{VERSION}\\"
"\\server\\\\odoo.conf`"
msgstr ""
"Конфигурационный файл находится в: `c:\\\\ProgramFiles\\\\Odoo{VERSION}\\\\s"
"erver\\\\odoo.conf`"

