"Use a package manager (`Homebrew <https://brew.sh/>`_, `MacPorts <https://"
"www.macports.org>`_) to download and install Python 3 if needed."
msgstr ""
"При необходимости используйте менеджер пакетов (`Homebrew <https://brew.sh/>"
