#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:305
msgid ""
"Odoo dependencies are listed in the :file:`requirements.txt` file located at "
"the root of the Odoo Community directory."
msgstr ""
"Зависимости Odoo перечислены в файле :file:`requirements.txt`, расположенном "
"в корне каталога Odoo Community."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:309
msgid ""
"The Python packages in :file:`requirements.txt` are based on their stable/"
"LTS Debian/Ubuntu corresponding version at the moment of the Odoo release. "
"For example, for Odoo 15.0, the `python3-babel` package version is 2.8.0 in "
"Debian Bullseye and 2.6.0 in Ubuntu Focal. The lowest version is then chosen "
"in the :file:`requirements.txt`."
msgstr ""
"Пакеты Python в :file:`requirements.txt` основаны на их стабильной/LTS "
"версии в Debian/Ubuntu на момент выпуска Odoo. Например, для Odoo 15.0 "
"версия пакета `python3-babel` составляет 2.8.0 в Debian Bullseye и 2.6.0 в "
"Ubuntu Focal. В :file:`requirements.txt` выбирается наименьшая версия."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:316
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:338
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:357
msgid ""
"It can be preferable not to mix Python module packages between different "
"instances of Odoo or with the system. However, it is possible to use "
"`virtualenv <https://pypi.org/project/virtualenv/>`_ to create isolated "
"Python environments."
msgstr ""
"Может быть предпочтительнее не смешивать пакеты модулей Python между "
"различными экземплярами Odoo или с системой. Однако можно использовать "
"`virtualenv <https://pypi.org/project/virtualenv/>`_ для создания "
"изолированных окружений Python."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:320
msgid ""
"Navigate to the path of the Odoo Community installation "
"(:file:`CommunityPath`) and run **pip** on the requirements file to install "
"the requirements for the current user."
msgstr ""
"Перейдите по пути установки Odoo Community (:file:`CommunityPath`) и "
"запустите **pip** для файла requirements, чтобы установить зависимости для "
"текущего пользователя."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:330
msgid ""
"Before installing the dependencies, download and install the `Build Tools "
"for Visual Studio <https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/downloads/>`_. Select "
"**C++ build tools** in the **Workloads** tab and install them when prompted."
msgstr ""
"Перед установкой зависимостей загрузите и установите `Build Tools for Visual "
"Studio <https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/downloads/>`_. Выберите **C++ "
"build tools** на вкладке **Workloads** и установите их при появлении запроса."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:334
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:353
msgid ""
"Odoo dependencies are listed in the `requirements.txt` file located at the "
"root of the Odoo Community directory."
msgstr ""
"Зависимости Odoo перечислены в файле `requirements.txt`, расположенном в "
"корне каталога Odoo Community."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:342
